                Nugget ice machines are popular in settings like fast-food
                restaurants and healthcare facilities due to the chewable, soft
                texture of the ice they produce. Known for their high production
                rates and energy efficiency, these machines are often in
                constant use. Common repair needs for nugget ice machines
